    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/d0e9bcc1f7a9565f3338849b3108a1e0.poster.avif?t=1686916778\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/d0e9bcc1f7a9565f3338849b3108a1e0.webm?t=1686916778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/d0e9bcc1f7a9565f3338849b3108a1e0.mp4?t=1686916778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Astralojia is a world in where everyone from your shopkeeper, teacher, or farmer practices martial arts and magic. It follows the story of the students of Raynwood Academy as they learn, grow, and discover the world of Astralojia and fight to the top of the rankings in a competitive school system. It's a slice-of-life fantasy, comedy, magic, drama series. The first season consists of the first 7 episodes, with plans for many future seasons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/b969b4731ad678471a241de78496e199.poster.avif?t=1686916778\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/b969b4731ad678471a241de78496e199.webm?t=1686916778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/b969b4731ad678471a241de78496e199.mp4?t=1686916778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BATTLES AND GAMEPLAY</h2><br>Astralojia are 'Story-and-Battle' games. You must clear battles and mini-games to progress the story. ATB turn-based battles have multiple modes throughout the episodes, from survival to timed health bar matches. Skill bars with multiple 'pitches' mean that it takes skill to clear battles, and each battle has a different aspect of strategy to proceed. The games are heavily story-based, consisting of key boss battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/e6e75906c92e3f7aad467274e5221e21.poster.avif?t=1686916778\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/e6e75906c92e3f7aad467274e5221e21.webm?t=1686916778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/e6e75906c92e3f7aad467274e5221e21.mp4?t=1686916778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOUNDTRACK</h2><br>The games have an 80s-esque rock and orchestral soundtrack inspired by japanese game and anime composers, as well as 70s, 80s and 90s era of film and television.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/838fa41b6307733fc3e4003ec6284907.poster.avif?t=1686916778\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/838fa41b6307733fc3e4003ec6284907.webm?t=1686916778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/838fa41b6307733fc3e4003ec6284907.mp4?t=1686916778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAKING OF</h2><br>With the exception of the sky boxes, trees, bushes, emoji bubbles, facesets and some Unity Assets, Astralojia: Season 1 was entirely created by a solo developer using C#/Unity, Photoshop for graphics and Reason for sound and music. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/6f6374a3d8fae6a47a646e38cdd7a7df.poster.avif?t=1686916778\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/6f6374a3d8fae6a47a646e38cdd7a7df.webm?t=1686916778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758480/extras/6f6374a3d8fae6a47a646e38cdd7a7df.mp4?t=1686916778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FULL VOICE ACTING</h2><br>The acting is performed by using Respeecher's A.I Voice Synthesis, so all genders of characters young and old were voiced by one individual.",
